  "title": "Hotel Concierge | 5 star hotel | 5 days",
  "description": "<p><u><strong>Concierge</strong></u><br /><u><strong>\n</strong></u><strong>Salary: $2,500 - $2,800 </strong><br /><strong>5 days work week, 44 hours (including weekends and PH)</strong><br /></p><p><strong>Rotating shift</strong></p><p><u><strong>Job Responsibilities</strong></u></p><ul><li>Assist guests with tour, restaurant, golf, and flight bookings and changes.</li><li>Provide directions and information on shopping, attractions, and places of interest.</li><li>Manage limousine bookings, assignments, billing, and revenue tracking.</li><li>Ensure hotel service, grooming, and quality standards are met.</li><li>Handle guest requests and complaints with empathy and suitable solutions.</li><li>Arrange pre-arrival requests such as birthdays, honeymoons, and anniversaries.</li><li>Make reservations for transport, flights, and theatre tickets.</li><li>Advise guests on visa, immigration, and customs requirements.</li><li>Handle calls, messages, lost and found, and ensure timely guest service follow-up.</li></ul><p><u><strong>Job Requirements</strong></u></p><ul><li>Prior experience in F&B/Retail or Service industry.</li><li>Able to read, write and speak English fluently to communicate with guest.</li><li>Friendly and engaging service attitude.</li><li>Good communication skills.</li><li>Interpersonal skills to deal with guests and colleagues.</li><li>Can do rotating shift.</li></ul><p><u><strong>Additional Benefits</strong></u></p><ul><li>AWS</li><li>Variable Bonus</li><li>Meals provided</li><li>Medical benefits </li><li>Birthday Leave </li><li>Annual leaves</li></ul><p><br /></p><p><strong>Hey Rocket Pte. Ltd. (EA 21C0816)</strong><br /><strong>Pui Hui Lee (R25127133)</strong></p>",
